            <li>Leading effective advocacy for policy change and strategic influence on policy decisions.</li>
            <li>Ensuring seamless delivery of services for the Commonwealth Scholarships and Fellowships Plan (CSFP) across six South Asian countries.</li>
            <li>Overseeing a portfolio of higher education and skill projects including capacity building, quality enhancement, and policy dialogues.</li>
